            From probability axioms to causal inference — every concept built for DS and AI engineers, with explicit math, real ML connections, and interview Q&A throughout.
          </p>
          <div class="rm-hero-tools">
            <span class="rm-tool-pill">scipy.stats</span><span class="rm-tool-pill">statsmodels</span><span class="rm-tool-pill">NumPy</span><span class="rm-tool-pill">pandas</span><span class="rm-tool-pill">pingouin</span><span class="rm-tool-pill">matplotlib</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <nav class="rm-hero-index" aria-label="Stage index">
